column1: Cuteness overload!! They are such beautiful and precious kittens!

I heard somewhere (probably kitten lady, which is an awesome youtuber) that brushing kittens with a toothbrush is to simulate their mother cleaning them. It's a nice thing to do if they have been separated from their mother to soon.
